# Plot Actogram data of a `tag`

This function display a plot of the acceleration time series recorded by
a tag

## Usage

``` r
plot_tag_actogram(tag, twl_offset = NULL, plot_plotly = FALSE)
```

## Arguments

- tag:

  a GeoPressureR `tag` object

- twl_offset:

  Shift of the middle of the night compared to 00:00 UTC (in hours). If
  not provided, it uses the middle of all nights.

- plot_plotly:

  logical to use `plotly`

## Value
